item.title: ZSM website
item.description: ZSM stands for Zespół Szkół Mechanicznych (rough tl: Mechanical School Complex). It’s a technical high-school in which I’ve got my IT mechanic degree. This project was part of apprenticeships. I was part of frontend developement team, mainly in part of design. Also I was in charge in makeing this website responsive.
